title: Kawaguesaga Lake
text: Kawaguesaga Lake is a lake in <a href="Oneida%20County%2C%20Wisconsin">Oneida County, Wisconsin</a> near <a href="Minocqua">Minocqua</a>. Its inflow and outflow is the <a href="Tomahawk%20River">Tomahawk River</a>. It is contiguous with <a href="Minocqua%20Lake">Minocqua Lake</a>.
